Package: refuginator
Title: An Interactive Tool for Identifying Refugia
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(given = "Nathaniel", family = "Morley", email = "nathaniel.morley2000@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0005-3816-1023"))
Description: A shiny-based web application for reconstructing organismal distributions and 
    identifying historical and geohistorical refugia using the methods recently 
    published by Morley et al. (2024, PNAS).
